    "title": "Front Office Manager - Yatra Hotels - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Front Office Manager with drive and ambition, Yatra Hotels in Gwalior is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Yatra Hotels:\nYatra Hotels is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Yatra Hotels!",
